        "created_at": "2025-11-21T11:04:05.296Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think this was done on purpose to reduce the risk of accidentally cancelling when trying to save the edit.</p>\n<p>Especially for people with larger fingers or limited coordination (which we can all be when on the go, typing one-handed), having “cancel” right next to “save” can be infuriating.  :)</p>",
